p;crop_width=1639&amp;v=1614947012&amp;width=1225 980w, //salt-yard.myshopify.com/cdn/shop/articles/Recorded_2048x_b1ee8bd3-5f84-41a6-9519-687daa176930.jpg?crop=region&amp;crop_height=921&amp;crop_left=204&amp;crop_top=0&amp;crop_width=1639&amp;v=1614947012&amp;width=1500 1200w, //salt-yard.myshopify.com/cdn/shop/articles/Recorded_2048x_b1ee8bd3-5f84-41a6-9519-687daa176930.jpg?crop=region&amp;crop_height=921&amp;crop_left=204&amp;crop_top=0&amp;crop_width=1639&amp;v=1614947012&amp;width=1750 1400w, //salt-yard.myshopify.com/cdn/shop/articles/Recorded_2048x_b1ee8bd3-5f84-41a6-9519-687daa176930.jpg?crop=region&amp;crop_height=921&amp;crop_left=204&amp;crop_top=0&amp;crop_width=1639&amp;v=1614947012&amp;width=2000 1600w, //salt-yard.myshopify.com/cdn/shop/articles/Recorded_2048x_b1ee8bd3-5f84-41a6-9519-687daa176930.jpg?crop=region&amp;crop_height=921&amp;crop_left=204&amp;crop_top=0&amp;crop_width=1639&amp;v=1614947012&amp;width=2400 1920w, //salt-yard.myshopify.com/cdn/shop/articles/Recorded_2048x_b1ee8bd3-5f84-41a6-9519-687daa176930.jpg?crop=region&amp;crop_height=921&amp;crop_left=204&amp;crop_top=0&amp;crop_width=1639&amp;v=1614947012&amp;width=2560 2048w\" class=\"theme-img\"></div>\n</a>\n        </div>\n      \n\n      <h2><a href=\"/blogs/magazine/from-unrecorded-to-recorded-deadstock-gets-a-new-lease-on-life\" title=\"\">From Unrecorded to Recorded: Deadstock gets a new lease on life.</a></h2>\n\n      <div class=\"meta meta--after-title small-text\">\n        \n          <div class=\"iconmeta time\">\n            \n              <time datetime=\"2021-03-05T12:23:31Z\">March 5, 2021</time>\n            \n            \n              —\n              <span class=\"author\">Clean Canvas</span>\n            \n          </div>\n        \n\n        \n          \n          \n            <div class=\"iconmeta tags\">\n              <span class=\"label\">Tagged:</span>\n              \n                <a href=\"/blogs/magazine/tagged/new-arrivals\" title=\"Show articles tagged New arrivals\">New arrivals</a>\n              \n            </div>\n          \n        \n      </div><div class=\"rte cf\"><meta charset=\"utf-8\"><span>Spawning from our principled outlook, we launched the Recorded collection. The aim to create awareness of today’s mass consumption and how disposable goods are inextricably linked to this phenomenon.</span>\n</div><div class=\"article__read-more-container\">\n        <a class=\"small-feature-link\" href=\"/blogs/magazine/from-unrecorded-to-recorded-deadstock-gets-a-new-lease-on-life\" aria-label=\"Read more: From Unrecorded to Recorded: Deadstock gets a new lease on life.\">Read more</a>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n\n  \n\n  <div class=\"article cc-animate-init cc-animate-in\" data-cc-animate=\"\">\n    <div class=\"article__inner \">\n      \n        <div class=\"article-image\">\n          <a href=\"/blogs/magazine/true-sustainability-is-quality-that-lasts-a-lifetime\"><div class=\"img-ar img-ar--cover\" style=\"--aspect-ratio: 1.78\">\n<img src=\"//salt-yard.myshopify.com/cdn/shop/articles/Unrecorded-store_2048x_7cc6a889-ae04-429d-90f5-0ddbe8a437fe.jpg?crop=region&amp;crop_height=921&amp;crop_left=204&amp;crop_top=0&amp;crop_width=1639&amp;v=1614946936&amp;width=2048\" alt=\"True sustainability is quality that lasts a lifetime.\" width=\"1639\" height=\"921\" loading=\"eager\" sizes=\"(min-width: 1024px) 440px, (min-width: 768px) 50vw, 100vw\" srcset=\"//salt-yard.myshopify.com/cdn/shop/articles/Unrecorded-store_2048x_7cc6a889-ae04-429d-90f5-0ddbe8a437fe.jpg?crop=region&amp;crop_height=921&amp;crop_left=204&amp;crop_top=0&amp;crop_width=1639&amp;v=1614946936&amp;width=425 340w, //salt-yard.myshopify.com/cdn/shop/articles/Unrecorded-store_2048x_7cc6a889-ae04-429d-90f5-0ddbe8a437fe.jpg?crop=region&amp;crop_height=921&amp;crop_left=204&amp;crop_top=0&amp;crop_width=1639&amp;v=1614946936&amp;width=600 480w, //salt-yard.myshopify.com/cdn/shop/articles/Unrecorded-store_2048x_7cc6a889-ae04-429d-90f5-